## ЁЯОп Key Patterns to Patterns-to-Problem Mapping

| If You See... | Think Pattern | Example Problems |
|---------------|---------------|------------------|
| States/Modes changing | State | ATM, Vending, Elevator |
| Multiple algorithms | Strategy | Payment, Pricing, Sorting |
| Add features dynamically | Decorator | Pizza, Coffee, Text Formatting |
| Only one instance | Singleton | Logger, DB Connection, Cache |
| Create different types | Factory | Vehicles, Documents, Notifications |
| Notify many objects | Observer | Pub-Sub, Stock Alerts, Events |
| Chain of handlers | Chain of Resp. | ATM cash, Logging, Validation |
| Tree/hierarchy | Composite | File System, Menu, Course Structure |
| Undo/Redo | Command | Text Editor, Transactions |

