## тЪая╕П Common Mistakes to Avoid

| Mistake | Better Approach |
|---------|-----------------|
| Starting to code immediately | Spend 10 min on clarifications |
| Overcomplicating | Start simple, add complexity |
| Ignoring edge cases | Ask about failures early |
| No demo/testing | Always show it works |
| Forgetting patterns | State, Strategy, Factory cover 70% |

